name: Blue Mosque
description:
This collection is one of my most valuable collections
Because I tested myself and combined 3 techniques in this work
First I started photographing historical places
After that, I started to do digital painting on photos digitally, and finally I made a calligraphy of the poem of the most famous poet of Tabriz on these historical works.
A lot of time has been spent on this
Each task may take about 30 hours
I am very happy to show this collection here
